CRC Credit Bureau Limited has appointed Ademola Adesalu as the Managing Director of its new subsidiary, CRC Data & Analytics Limited. This appointment, which took effect from January 1, this year, is in furtherance to CRC operating under a group structure with diversified business interests in credit reporting, and data  and analytics.   FDIs to rise as West Africa Automative Show returns     GTCo, Fidelity CEOs, others honoured     Polaris Bank stresses need for savings culture among youths   Adesalu will oversee the growing team of data analytics experts and manage the processes and people responsible for accurate data collection, processing, modelling and analysis. Group Managing Director/CEO of CRC Credit Bureau Limited,  ‘Tunde Popoola, stated: “Adesalu has been an integral part of CRC’s growth since its inception in 2008. He led the team that set up our infrastructure solution in 2008 and has brought a wide-ranging data-backed experience focused around several key industries making him the best man for the job.”